<p>Pulling down huts &amp; tents; preparing to move from here shortly</p>
<p>23.1.17<br/>Awfully cold, everything frozen, even the medicines in the bottles are one block of ice.  Discharged from hospital; sick &amp; tired of being indoors.  All the ponds in the vicinity covered with ice. Cable arrived from home, Birthday greetings.</p>
<p>Wednesday 24.1 17<br/>Some of the boys tried their hand at skating on the ice, but before the day was out there was quite a number of accidents through falls. Yesterday reported as coldest day in France since the beginning of the war.</p>
